### 2. **Cross-Site Scripting (XSS)** (Would be flagged ❌)
```javascript
// BAD - Would be detected by CodeQL
function displayUserInput(input) {
  document.innerHTML = input; // Dangerous!
}

// GOOD - Safe rendering
